==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: tiānshēng wŏ cái bì yŏuyòng
===Proverb===
'''[[天生]][[我]][[才]][[必]][[有用]]'''
# Everybody has something that they were born to be good at; if you search hard enough, you will find your niche in life.
